	Arduino PicasoSGC Library:
	============================================================================
	Download latest source of the library at:
	https://github.com/tklenke/Picaso_SGM

	Instalation
	============================================================================
	Install folder Picaso_SGC into Arduino Libraries folder 
		(required files are picaso_sgc.h and picaso_sgc.cpp)	

	Tested on the Arduino IDE 1.0, Arduino Uno and 4DSystems µVGA-II(SGC)

	General information
	============================================================================
	Usage:  #include <picaso_sgc.h> in your project.  See included example.
	
